OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FITV News' Chris Hall looks back on the
OL,7,Flife of legendary footballer and
OL,8,Fmanager Kevin Keegan.
OL,10,FFormer England footballer and manager
OL,11,FKevin Keegan has died at the age of 75.
OL,13,FIn a statement, his family said: "It
OL,14,Fis with immense sadness that we
OL,15,Fannounce that Kevin Keegan has passed
OL,16,Faway at the age of 75. The former
OL,17,FEngland player and manager had been
OL,18,Fbattling cancer and was surrounded by
OL,19,Fhis wife and daughters in his final
OL,20,Fmoments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Kevin, a double Ballon D'or winner,
OL,7,Fwas a much loved husband, father and
OL,8,Fgrandfather. The family would like to
OL,9,Fthank Kevin's incredible medical team
OL,10,Ffor all their support.
OL,12,F"This is a hugely difficult time and
OL,13,Fthey are requesting space and privacy."
OL,15,FThe former Liverpool player and
OL,16,FNewcastle manager revealed he had
OL,17,Fcancer in January 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
