CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FSpeaking in May, Keegan told an
OL,7,Faudience he was responding well to
OL,8,Ftreatment after being assured "'we
OL,9,Fhave a top doctor with this new way of
OL,10,Ffighting what you have got".
OL,12,F"He (the doctor) was a Liverpool
OL,13,Fsupporter, so I went to meet him. I
OL,14,Fknew I wouldn't be walking alone, if
OL,15,Fyou know what I mean."
OL,26,@tD@EpmtD@Ppn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
