OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FA statement from Liverpool FC said:
OL,7,F"We are deeply saddened by the passing
OL,8,Fof the legendary Kevin Keegan and
OL,9,Fmourn his loss. His indomitable spirit
OL,10,Fand remarkable contribution will be
OL,11,Fforever etched in our history and his
OL,12,Flegacy will live on."
OL,14,FA statement from the England National
OL,15,Fteam said: "We are incredibly saddened
OL,16,Fby the news that Kevin Keegan OBE has
OL,17,Fpassed away.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Kevin earned 63 international caps
OL,7,Fand scored 21 goals between 1972 and
OL,8,F1982, before managing the _ThreeLions
OL,9,Ffrom 1999 to 2000.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts and condolences are with
OL,12,FKevin's family, friends and former
OL,13,Fclubs."
OL,15,FA statement from Newcastle United
OL,16,Fcalled Keegan "the beating heart of
OL,17,Fthe club for generations of supporters"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FIt said: "As a player, he brought
OL,7,Fworld-class talent, ambition and
OL,8,Fbelief to St. James' Park, helping to
OL,9,Ftransform perceptions of what
OL,10,FNewcastle United could be.
OL,12,F"As a manager, he ignited our city.
OL,13,FKevin gave supporters hope and pride,
OL,14,Fand led a team whose style, spirit and
OL,15,Fpassion captured the imagination of
OL,16,Ffootball fans around the world. He was
OL,17,Fso much more than an Entertainer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Above all that, Kevin forged an
OL,7,Fextraordinary bond with Newcastle,
OL,8,Fbuilt on the roots of his father, Joe.
OL,9,FHe understood our people. He embraced
OL,10,Fthe North East with a passion that was
OL,11,Fgenuine and unwavering, and in return,
OL,12,Fhe earned his rightful place in the
OL,13,Fhearts of millions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Kevin's impact will not be measured
OL,7,Fby appearances or results. It will
OL,8,Flive on in the memories he created
OL,9,Fwith club and country, the dreams he
OL,10,Finspired wherever he went, and the
OL,11,Fgenerations of supporters around the
OL,12,Fworld who fell in love with football
OL,13,Fbecause of him.
OL,15,F"At this profoundly sad time, we send
OL,16,Four love and deepest sympathy to
OL,17,FKevin's wife Jean, his family, friends
OL,18,Fand all who had the privilege of
OL,19,Fknowing and working alongside him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Today, we mourn the loss of a true
OL,7,Fgiant of our history, and at the
OL,8,Fappropriate moment, we will carefully
OL,9,Fconsider how we shape a lasting
OL,10,Ftribute to Kevin's remarkable life and
OL,11,Flegacy.
OL,13,F"Rest in peace, King Kev."
OL,15,FKeegan - born in Armthorpe, Doncaster
OL,16,F- began his career with Scunthorpe and
OL,17,Fwas signed by Liverpool in 1971,
OL,18,Fwinning the First Division three times
OL,19,Falong with two UEFA Cups, the FA Cup
OL,20,Fand the 1977 European Cup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784576903
OL,3,CFootballer and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FHe won the Ballon d'Or ` then called
OL,7,Fthe European Footballer of the Year `
OL,8,Ftwice while at German side Hamburg,
OL,9,Fwhere he featured in another European
OL,10,FCup final, and played for Southampton
OL,11,Fand Newcastle before retiring in 1984.
OL,13,FOn the international stage, he scored
OL,14,F21 goals in 63 England appearances and
OL,15,Fplayed at the 1982 World Cup finals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
